20:15.680 --> 20:19.640
I don't care if they hassle me
about my work, but my family?

20:19.800 --> 20:22.520
Just as well
I'm the bunny in the headlights

20:22.640 --> 20:25.320
doing the vasilich appeal, isn't it?

20:25.440 --> 20:27.440
That's the golden lining, is it?

20:30.760 --> 20:33.600
