20:42.440 --> 20:44.080
Friends.
I know. Friends.

20:44.240 --> 20:45.840
You and I
spend a lot of time together.

20:46.000 --> 20:47.800
You and Janet hugged.
So have you and I!

20:47.920 --> 20:49.280
But I'm not gay.

20:49.440 --> 20:52.240
Because it's Janet, it's
