this new evidence means

24:04.080 --> 24:07.040
this conviction was, one,
unsafe or unsatisfactory,

24:07.160 --> 24:08.640
two, was wrong in law

24:08.800 --> 24:10.880
or three, constituted
a miscarriage of justice.

24:11.040 --> 24:13.080
You don't need me.
