26:43.240 --> 26:45.560
You still have prints of the photos
from this website?

26:45.720 --> 26:48.800
Boxes and boxes of them.
Could I borrow them this morning?

26:48.920 --> 26:51.320
And the website address.

26:51.480 --> 26:54.040
This photo was taken near
the lighthouse in point Galloway.

26:54.200 --> 26:56.400
On the South coast?
