was on the selection panel?

30:52.280 --> 30:54.520
One of three, yes.

30:54.640 --> 30:56.840
You see each other socially?

30:57.000 --> 31:00.480
Yes. There's nothing
wrong with that, is there?

31:02.120 --> 31:04.160
When did you discover that
you and miss king

31:04.280 --> 31:08.760
